title: AMERICAN GODS Season 2 Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: Hearing lots of differing opinions about this season. What did you guys think?
We need more Anansi/Mr Nancy next season. The actor has been phenomenal with little he's been given these 2 seasons.

In my opinion: This feels like a filler season. They spent the entire season trying to get dead wife alive, and fix Odin's spear. Well Odin's spear is gone and dead wife is still rotting. Along with the profound metaphors, very minimal plot advancements and minor character development it really didn't feel we got far into the story whatsoever especially when it takes them a long time to release new seasons.
This season went by way too quick 😭😭
"Man created God in his own image " Best Lesson from the episode!
description:
We breakdown the season 2 finale of American Gods "Moon Shadow" and take a deep dive into the mythology and details you may have missed.
